summary.purpose: Provides a set of inline JSX SVG and icon constants for common vehicle dashboard warning indicators including low fuel, battery, tyre pressure, ABS, airbag, check engine, and charging state â€” in both compact and full-size variants.
summary.problem_solved: Centralises vehicle warning icon assets so that dashboard and alert UI components can import ready-to-use warning icons without embedding raw SVG markup inline.

symbols.name: bellIco
symbols.description_one_line: Inline JSX icon for a bell notification indicator with yellow styling.

details.what_it_does: A pre-rendered JSX div containing a FontAwesome solid bell icon (fa-sharp fa-solid fa-bell) in yellow (#F5D00A). Used as a notification or alarm indicator in vehicle dashboard warning lists.

symbols.name: low_fuel_levelSvg
symbols.description_one_line: Inline SVG constant for a low fuel level warning indicator (yellow).

details.what_it_does: A pre-rendered JSX SVG element (11x12 px) depicting a fuel pump symbol in yellow (#F5D00A). Used in compact vehicle dashboard warning lists to indicate low fuel.

symbols.name: batterySvg
symbols.description_one_line: Inline SVG constant for a battery warning indicator (yellow).

details.what_it_does: A pre-rendered JSX SVG element (18x12 px) depicting a car battery symbol in yellow (#F5D00A). Used in compact vehicle dashboard warning lists to indicate a battery fault.

symbols.name: low_airSvg
symbols.description_one_line: Inline SVG constant for a low tyre pressure warning indicator (yellow).

details.what_it_does: A pre-rendered JSX SVG element (14x12 px) depicting a tyre pressure / flat tyre symbol in yellow (#F5D00A). Used in compact vehicle dashboard warning lists to indicate low tyre pressure.

symbols.name: absSvg
symbols.description_one_line: Inline SVG constant for an ABS warning indicator (yellow).

details.what_it_does: A pre-rendered JSX SVG element (19x12 px) depicting an ABS anti-lock braking symbol in yellow (#F5D00A). Used in compact vehicle dashboard warning lists to indicate an ABS fault.

symbols.name: air_bagSvg
symbols.description_one_line: Inline SVG constant for an airbag warning indicator (yellow).

details.what_it_does: A pre-rendered JSX SVG element depicting an airbag/SRS warning symbol in yellow (#F5D00A). Used in compact vehicle dashboard warning lists to indicate an airbag fault.

symbols.name: check_engineSvg
symbols.description_one_line: Inline SVG constant for a check engine warning indicator (yellow).

details.what_it_does: A pre-rendered JSX SVG element depicting an engine/check-engine symbol in yellow (#F5D00A). Used in compact vehicle dashboard warning lists to indicate an engine fault.

symbols.name: low_battery_level_svg
symbols.description_one_line: Inline SVG constant for a low battery level warning indicator (yellow).

details.what_it_does: A pre-rendered JSX SVG element depicting a low-charge battery symbol in yellow (#F5D00A). Used in compact vehicle dashboard warning lists to indicate a low battery charge level.

symbols.name: charging_icon
symbols.description_one_line: Inline JSX FontAwesome bolt icon representing a charging state (green).

details.what_it_does: A pre-rendered JSX element using a FontAwesome regular bolt icon (fa-regular fa-bolt) in green (#37a744). Used in compact vehicle dashboard warning lists to indicate that the vehicle is charging.

symbols.name: site_low_fuel_levelSvg
symbols.description_one_line: Full-size SVG constant for a low fuel level warning indicator for site-level display (yellow).

details.what_it_does: A larger pre-rendered JSX SVG element of a fuel pump symbol in yellow. Used in site-level vehicle alert panels where more space is available compared to the compact bellIco-series icons.
